Comprehensive Python library for analyzing higher-order interaction networks including hypergraphs and simplicial complexes.

[Download paper here](https://joss.theoj.org/papers/10.21105/joss.05162) | [Code](https://github.com/xgi-org/xgi) | [Documentation](https://xgi.readthedocs.io/)
